+------+-------+----------+-------------------------+


+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
; Port Connectivity Checks: "Timer:pt|Bin_to_BCD:B1"                                                                                                                                                             ;
+---------+--------+----------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
; Port    ; Type   ; Severity ; Details                                                                                                                                                                          ;
+---------+--------+----------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
